entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Animal yo pap atackè jou funeral ou. Mwen sèten." t="Animals won't pounce the day of the funeral. I'm positive." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwe ap mouri isit la?" t="I'm dyin' out here." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="O, wi? Soti nan kisa, respè?" t="Oh, yeah? Outta what, respect?" b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="creo" o="Non kalm'n boss papa. Yo menm yo nan èkondisyone. Se nou menm ki ap transpirasye tankou bourik." t="No calm down boss. They are in air conditioning. We're the ones sweating like donkeys." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Non, gèt manman ou. Tann, ki jan ou jwenn enfòmasyon sou A / C a?" t="No, fuck off. Wait, how d'you find out about the A/C?" b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="creo" o="Jeff te vin tou pre yè swa. Li tande jeneratè a, um panse ke Animal yo te dwe fè li mache." t="Jeff got reeeeal close last night. Heard the generator, Animals must've got it running." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Pakèt salopri?" t="Motherfuckers." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="E pa fòt solèy la. Fou ou dòmi plis, man." t="Not the sun's fault. You gotta get more sleep, man." b="" a=""/>
